              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīmatparamahaṃsaparivrājakācāryaśrīmadgoviṃdabhagavatpūjyapādaśiṣyeṇa śrīśaṃkarācāryeṇa kṛtam īśāvāsyabhāṣyaṃ saṃpūrṇaṃ // (f. 15r).</colophon>
